USCafes Limited partnership say e complete di sale of im Bonanza restaurant franchise to one subsidiary of Metromedia Co, for $71 million in cash.

UUSACafes (wey nearly reach half owned by Sam and Charles Wyly of Dallas) talk sey e go sell di sale to unit holders as liquidation dividend as soon as possible.

Di Bonanza franchise system, wey dey generate about $600 million each year, na most of di partnership asset be that.

Di sale of system system don begin for one class action suit on top of unit holders wey dem bin file last week for Delaware court, USACafes yarn.

Di company yarn sey di suit no get merit.

